#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.184"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.184:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.184:0.2"
msgid "19. Brāhmaṇavagga "
msgstr "19. Brahmins "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: jāṇussonīsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.184:0.3"
msgid "184. Abhayasutta "
msgstr "184. Fearless "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: jāṇussoṇi → jāṇussonī (bj)
msgctxt "an4.184:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then the brahmin Jāṇussoṇi went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "an4.184:1.2"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side and said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.184:2.1"
msgid "“Ahañhi, bho gotama, evaṃvādī evaṃdiṭṭhi: "
msgstr "“Master Gotama, this is my doctrine and view: "

msgctxt "an4.184:2.2"
msgid "‘natthi yo maraṇadhammo samāno na bhāyati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassā’”ti. "
msgstr "‘All those liable to death are frightened and terrified of death.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.184:2.3"
msgid "“Atthi, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno bhāyati, santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa; "
msgstr "“Brahmin, some of those liable to death are frightened and terrified of death. "

msgctxt "an4.184:2.4"
msgid "atthi pana, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno na bhāyati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa. "
msgstr "But some of those liable to death are not frightened and terrified of death. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.174, sc3
msgctxt "an4.184:3.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno bhāyati, santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa? "
msgstr "Who are those frightened of death? "

msgctxt "an4.184:3.2"
msgid "Idha, brāhmaṇa, ekacco kāmesu avītarāgo hoti avigatacchando avigatapemo avigatapipāso avigatapariḷāho avigatataṇho. "
msgstr "It’s someone who isn’t free of greed, desire, fondness, thirst, passion, and craving for sensual pleasures. "

msgctxt "an4.184:3.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati. "
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill, "

msgctxt "an4.184:3.4"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "they think: "

msgctxt "an4.184:3.5"
msgid "‘piyā vata maṃ kāmā jahissanti, piye cāhaṃ kāme jahissāmī’ti. "
msgstr "‘The sensual pleasures that I love so much will leave me, and I’ll leave them.’ "

msgctxt "an4.184:3.6"
msgid "So socati kilamati paridevati, urattāḷiṃ kandati, sammohaṃ āpajjati. "
msgstr "They sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into confusion. "

msgctxt "an4.184:3.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno bhāyati, santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa. "
msgstr "This is someone who is frightened of death. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.184:4.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco kāye avītarāgo hoti avigatacchando avigatapemo avigatapipāso avigatapariḷāho avigatataṇho. "
msgstr "Furthermore, it’s someone who isn’t free of greed, desire, fondness, thirst, passion, and craving for the body. "

msgctxt "an4.184:4.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati. "
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill, "

msgctxt "an4.184:4.3"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "they think: "

msgctxt "an4.184:4.4"
msgid "‘piyo vata maṃ kāyo jahissati, piyañcāhaṃ kāyaṃ jahissāmī’ti. "
msgstr "‘This body that I love so much will leave me, and I’ll leave it.’ "

msgctxt "an4.184:4.5"
msgid "So socati kilamati paridevati, urattāḷiṃ kandati, sammohaṃ āpajjati. "
msgstr "They sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into confusion. "

msgctxt "an4.184:4.6"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno bhāyati, santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa. "
msgstr "This, too, is someone who is frightened of death. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.184:5.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco akatakalyāṇo hoti akatakusalo akatabhīruttāṇo katapāpo kataluddo katakibbiso. "
msgstr "Furthermore, it’s someone who hasn’t done good and skillful things that keep them safe, but has done bad, violent, and corrupt things. "

msgctxt "an4.184:5.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati. "
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill, "

msgctxt "an4.184:5.3"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "they think: "

msgctxt "an4.184:5.4"
msgid "‘akataṃ vata me kalyāṇaṃ, akataṃ kusalaṃ, akataṃ bhīruttāṇaṃ; "
msgstr "‘Well, I haven’t done good and skillful things that keep me safe. "

msgctxt "an4.184:5.5"
msgid "kataṃ pāpaṃ, kataṃ luddaṃ, kataṃ kibbisaṃ. "
msgstr "And I have done bad, violent, and corrupt things. "

msgctxt "an4.184:5.6"
msgid "Yāvatā, bho, akatakalyāṇānaṃ akatakusalānaṃ akatabhīruttāṇānaṃ katapāpānaṃ kataluddānaṃ katakibbisānaṃ gati taṃ gatiṃ pecca gacchāmī’ti. "
msgstr "When I depart, I’ll go to the place where people who’ve done such things go.’ "

msgctxt "an4.184:5.7"
msgid "So socati kilamati paridevati, urattāḷiṃ kandati, sammohaṃ āpajjati. "
msgstr "They sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into confusion. "

msgctxt "an4.184:5.8"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno bhāyati, santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa. "
msgstr "This, too, is someone who is frightened of death. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an4.184:6.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco kaṅkhī hoti vicikicchī aniṭṭhaṅgato saddhamme. "
msgstr "Furthermore, it’s someone who’s doubtful, uncertain, and undecided about the true teaching. "

msgctxt "an4.184:6.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati. "
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill, "

msgctxt "an4.184:6.3"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "they think: "

msgctxt "an4.184:6.4"
msgid "‘kaṅkhī vatamhi vicikicchī aniṭṭhaṅgato saddhamme’ti. "
msgstr "‘I’m doubtful, uncertain, and undecided about the true teaching.’ "

msgctxt "an4.184:6.5"
msgid "So socati kilamati paridevati, urattāḷiṃ kandati, sammohaṃ āpajjati. "
msgstr "They sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into confusion. "

msgctxt "an4.184:6.6"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno bhāyati, santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa. "
msgstr "This, too, is someone who is frightened of death. "

msgctxt "an4.184:6.7"
msgid "Ime kho, brāhmaṇa, cattāro maraṇadhammā samānā bhāyanti, santāsaṃ āpajjanti maraṇassa. "
msgstr "These are the four people liable to death who are frightened and terrified of death. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.175, sc7
msgctxt "an4.184:7.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno na bhāyati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa? "
msgstr "Who are those not frightened of death? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.184:7.2"
msgid "Idha, brāhmaṇa, ekacco kāmesu vītarāgo hoti vigatacchando vigatapemo vigatapipāso vigatapariḷāho vigatataṇho. "
msgstr "It’s someone who is rid of greed, desire, fondness, thirst, passion, and craving for sensual pleasures. "

msgctxt "an4.184:7.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati. "
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill, "

msgctxt "an4.184:7.4"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa na evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "they don’t think: "

msgctxt "an4.184:7.5"
msgid "‘piyā vata maṃ kāmā jahissanti, piye cāhaṃ kāme jahissāmī’ti. "
msgstr "‘The sensual pleasures that I love so much will leave me, and I’ll leave them.’ "

msgctxt "an4.184:7.6"
msgid "So na socati na kilamati na paridevati, na urattāḷiṃ kandati, na sammohaṃ āpajjati. "
msgstr "They don’t sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into confusion. "

msgctxt "an4.184:7.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno na bhāyati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa. "
msgstr "This is someone who’s not frightened of death. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an4.184:8.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco kāye vītarāgo hoti vigatacchando vigatapemo vigatapipāso vigatapariḷāho vigatataṇho. "
msgstr "Furthermore, it’s someone who is rid of greed, desire, fondness, thirst, passion, and craving for the body. "

msgctxt "an4.184:8.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati. "
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill, "

msgctxt "an4.184:8.3"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa na evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "they don’t think: "

msgctxt "an4.184:8.4"
msgid "‘piyo vata maṃ kāyo jahissati, piyañcāhaṃ kāyaṃ jahissāmī’ti. "
msgstr "‘This body that I love so much will leave me, and I’ll leave it.’ "

msgctxt "an4.184:8.5"
msgid "So na socati na kilamati na paridevati, na urattāḷiṃ kandati, na sammohaṃ āpajjati. "
msgstr "They don’t sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into confusion. "

msgctxt "an4.184:8.6"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno na bhāyati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa. "
msgstr "This, too, is someone who’s not frightened of death. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an4.184:9.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco akatapāpo hoti akataluddo akatakibbiso katakalyāṇo katakusalo katabhīruttāṇo. "
msgstr "Furthermore, it’s someone who hasn’t done bad, violent, and corrupt deeds, but has done good and skillful deeds that keep them safe. "

msgctxt "an4.184:9.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati. "
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill, "

msgctxt "an4.184:9.3"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "they think: "

msgctxt "an4.184:9.4"
msgid "‘akataṃ vata me pāpaṃ, akataṃ luddaṃ, akataṃ kibbisaṃ; "
msgstr "‘Well, I haven’t done bad, violent, and corrupt things. "

msgctxt "an4.184:9.5"
msgid "kataṃ kalyāṇaṃ, kataṃ kusalaṃ, kataṃ bhīruttāṇaṃ. "
msgstr "And I have done good and skillful deeds that keep me safe. "

msgctxt "an4.184:9.6"
msgid "Yāvatā, bho, akatapāpānaṃ akataluddānaṃ akatakibbisānaṃ katakalyāṇānaṃ katakusalānaṃ katabhīruttāṇānaṃ gati taṃ gatiṃ pecca gacchāmī’ti. "
msgstr "When I depart, I’ll go to the place where people who’ve done such things go.’ "

msgctxt "an4.184:9.7"
msgid "So na socati na kilamati na paridevati, na urattāḷiṃ kandati, na sammohaṃ āpajjati. "
msgstr "They don’t sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into confusion. "

msgctxt "an4.184:9.8"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno na bhāyati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa. "
msgstr "This, too, is someone who’s not frightened of death. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.176, sc10
msgctxt "an4.184:10.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco akaṅkhī hoti avicikicchī niṭṭhaṅgato saddhamme. "
msgstr "Furthermore, it’s someone who’s not doubtful, uncertain, or undecided about the true teaching. "

msgctxt "an4.184:10.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ aññataro gāḷho rogātaṅko phusati. "
msgstr "When they fall seriously ill, "

msgctxt "an4.184:10.3"
msgid "Tassa aññatarena gāḷhena rogātaṅkena phuṭṭhassa evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "they think: "

msgctxt "an4.184:10.4"
msgid "‘akaṅkhī vatamhi avicikicchī niṭṭhaṅgato saddhamme’ti. "
msgstr "‘I’m not doubtful, uncertain, or undecided about the true teaching.’ "

msgctxt "an4.184:10.5"
msgid "So na socati na kilamati na paridevati, na urattāḷiṃ kandati, na sammohaṃ āpajjati. "
msgstr "They don’t sorrow and wail and lament, beating their breast and falling into confusion. "

msgctxt "an4.184:10.6"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, maraṇadhammo samāno na bhāyati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati maraṇassa. "
msgstr "This, too, is someone who’s not frightened of death. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.184:10.7"
msgid "Ime kho, brāhmaṇa, cattāro maraṇadhammā samānā na bhāyanti, na santāsaṃ āpajjanti maraṇassā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four people liable to death who are not frightened and terrified of death.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an4.184:11.1"
msgid "“Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! … From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.184:11.2"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

